(301, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=2b3e2a6fa44dd33674b381a6a104e25f7326c7a4921b78109b51d12d2ac26006', 'Georgioupolis Hügeln - gross', '50', '68', '水彩', '復古', 'Karina Plachetka', 2019, 'Green', 82800, 'Georgioupolis 地區被連綿起伏的丘陵所環繞。在前往克里特島和希臘的旅行中觀察到', 'F'),
(302, 'https://sh-cdn.singulart.?signature=5b606ac0043a8cb0eeb0be1468291751364c839752b1ddbf52c5e2a5528ff0fa', 'Griechischer Mauer', '80', '100', '油畫', '超現實', 'Karina Plachetka', 2002, 'White', 211600, '古希臘城牆。在古埃及、美索不達米亞和歐洲就存在繪畫中描繪風景圖案的證據', 'F'),
